I'm not sure how I can come out like this, or how to even fabricate my unorthodox emotions into words. But here goes; I am a minion.

Every morning I meet up with my friends, and say "bello". The looks of despair I am greeted with mixed with the utmost disgust upsets me deeply. Just because I speak minionease.

I look in the mirror and shed a tear as I wish I was 4 feet smaller, and had only 1 eye. Kevin, Stuart and even Bob to an extent have always been role models of mine due to how well they act and the humour they exhibit.

Please don't be a hater and say that I am a troll punk, because even us minions have feelings too.

A map that took over three months on and off. The last time I ran it it took me around four minutes, I hope that someone get a time way lower than mine. I tried to make a map around a theme, that of a dungeon, and I think it turned out alright. 

Also this map has some hard longjumps, the first 250 unit longjump can be skipped if you're fast enough.

Even though I would love to have a CS:GO port out today, the map is really dark for some reason and it won't be posted until that gets fixed. (Any help would be appreciated.)

For around 10 months ago, i released my first project bhop_dreamtour. The purpose was to make a hard auto map, and also the longest bhop map ever made. As long as i created the levels, i didn't know very much about compiling and optimizing a level, which caused i had to cut the map into 2 maps, and release bhop_dreamtour2 in a couple of time afterwards.

Now i have remade some parts in the map, and added some more detail to it, but a lot of the map was builded 10 month ago, so i had to make the environment roughly based on the rooms/creations.

I have remade this map to be PLAYED ON LEGIT! since it will be too linear with the autobhop gameplay it had, as the very first time.

It has different non in-real-life themes as bhop_dreamtour has. and the difficulty is pretty hard overall. It starts a little easier and gets harder through the levels and stages. Some stages is a bit long.

It can be played on normal scroll/legit settings with 100 tickrate, sv_airaccelerate 100, sv_gravity 800, fps_max 300 and no scout/260 ground speed, but also good gameplay for autobhop settings 100 tickrate.

Thanks for George and Dream for testing the levels. have fun.

Map made across the week, thanks to Pcpie for solving my problems when I had them. Happens quite often.

I made most of the map on stream (http://twitch.tv/dreeeaam), check out some of the past broadcasts if you are that interested in watching me make this. I plan to do more streams with more maps for the future but my internet is not stable so the viewers do not have much enjoyment from it.

NOTE: the start is where you spawn, when you reach the "go back" section, you turn around and go back through the map a little. Just trying to experiment with some new gameplay that has been used a lot recently.

I will try and make my next map textured, I have been trying a  lot recently to use realistic textures but my style of mapping just makes it really difficult for me.
